+++++ [[span class="cond"]]__Employee Guidelines: The Basics__[[/span]]

[[span class="cond"]]On your first day as Foundation personnel, it's important that you familiarize yourself with the way our organization is, well, organized! Everything from contacting your supervisor to ordering tests, performing said tests and disposing of waste materials—they all have procedures to follow! Not only that, but they all have hardworking people, just like yourself, behind the scenes. It is integral that we all do our part, and that includes knowing when to pass the baton on to the next person. This keeps your secure site moving smoothly like a well-oiled machine![[/span]]

[[span class="cond"]]The[[/span]] [[span class="conds"]]FOUNDATION EMPLOYEE AXIOMS[[/span]][[span class="cond"]] are an effective means to remind everyone of the roles they play in our workplace, with hope that {{THE FOUNDER}}'s guiding light shines through us, even in the dark:[[/span]]
@@ @@
@@ @@
▪︎ [[span class="cond"]]All employees have purpose. They are the foundation of the Foundation[[/span]]
▪︎ [[span class="cond"]]All employees report from an assigned Secure Facility[[/span]]
▪︎ [[span class="cond"]]Each Secure Facility has a Site Director[[/span]]
▪︎ [[span class="cond"]]Each Department has a Director of Operations[[/span]]
▪︎ [[span class="cond"]]Every onsite employee is assigned a Department[[/span]]
▪︎ [[span class="cond"]]Every employee has a voice and a right to be heard[[/span]][[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]Replaced in //Second Edition// with "Every employee has a right to an appeals process" before being completely removed in //Fourth Edition//.[[/span]]
▪︎ [[span class="cond"]]Every employee does their part, allowing others to do the same[[/span]]
▪︎ [[span class="cond"]]Employees will behave in a manner becoming of them, or __they will be replaced__[[/span]]
