**LOCATION:** {{Site-19 Briefing Room 8A}}

**PARTIES PRESENT:**

* {{Director Ruaidhri Quade, Site-19 Department of Notional Divisions }}
* {{Class-C Personnel James Anselm Harkness (PoI-8190)}}
