[[span class="st"]]ADDENDUM 8190-A/1:[[/span]] Interview II
[[div class="leaf" style="width: 88%; margin-bottom:8px;"]]
[[image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-8190/wheel3.gif width="116px" style="padding-top:17px; padding-bottom:17px;"]]
